### list bucket files

GET http://localhost:8000/api/files/listFileInBucket/tutorial-images HTTP/1.1


### 


### get file

GET http://localhost:8000/api/files/fileUrl/tutorial-images/sample3.png HTTP/1.1


### 


### make bucket public

POST http://localhost:8000/adminApi/files/makeBucketPublic/tutorial-images HTTP/1.1


### 


### upload file

POST http://localhost:8000/adminApi/files/uploadFile HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="fileName"

test1
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="bucketName"

tutorial-images
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample3.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ~/Pictures/wallpapers/5042431.jpg

------WebKitFormBoundary--


